summary: A new modified version of Breezehome.
descriptionHtml:
I have create a new version of my favorite home.

List of modifications :
- Existing furniture rearranged.
- More containers.
- A new bedroom.
- A modified Alchemy Lab.
- An enchant and alchemy lab when you buy the childs bedroom.

Heartfire require.
No additionnals contents.
Compatible with mods that do not interfere with breezehome cell.

Version 1.1 : A little problem with the housecarl room walls Fixed.

Version 1.2 : A little problem with the loft wall Fixed. Add some candle.
author: beronar
